{"tid":1066412,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"曾幾何時地鐵瀨屎係一個笑話","createTime":"2019-03-18T01:30:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-24T08:44:45.000Z","uid":2156,"like":69,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e5217aba14a923bfc4fc6ead219b1063dfe78a6d","tid":1066412,"uid":2156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T01:30:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eUX98wH.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeUX98wH.gif&h=5c79bc55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n曾經，啲人遲到，用地鐵塞車做藉口，我哋心入面會屌鳩佢遲到搵個好啲嘅藉口啦<br />\n<br />\n今日，地鐵炒車<br />\n狗鐵慚唔慚愧知唔知羞？<br />\n得香港人會鬧港鐵？<br />\n人唔笑狗都吠啦<br />\n<br />\n香港有三大笑話<br />\n1.香港政府<br />\n2.香港法治<br />\n3.香港鐵路<br />\n<br />\n地鐵諗住塞車&gt;炒車&gt;冧月台，循序漸進，向中國睇齊"},{"pid":"322598c529319e6c55f5d6461553c1637aefbe10","tid":1066412,"uid":62935,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T01:32:15.000Z","msg":"以前約人遲到話 sorry 地鐵塞車<br />\n係笑話<br />\n<br />\n而家耐唔時就一單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35a42dc43255152d061d9e02889688ff5e441c15","tid":1066412,"uid":189157,"like":3,"dislike":21,"score":-18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T01:32:20.000Z","msg":"地鐵撞車唔識早啲出門口?<br />\n預早3個鍾撞乜都一定可以準時返到啦"},{"pid":"7357c43994bebbf4be766906d4acbdfed677d375","tid":1066412,"uid":2156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"322598c529319e6c55f5d6461553c1637aefbe10","tid":1066412,"uid":62935,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T01:32:15.000Z","msg":"以前約人遲到話 sorry 地鐵塞車<br />\n係笑話<br />\n<br />\n而家耐唔時就一單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T01:40:17.000Z","msg":"依加啲人可以多個藉口遲到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n地鐵炒車好出奇呀？"},{"pid":"8cd5727caebf0462eae8382ea934845bff8d8a9f","tid":1066412,"uid":9726,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T01:42:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8